  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="NA49-kiḷavi">1. itu tōḻi talaimakaḷai yiravukkuṟi nayappittatu. 2. itu ciṟaippuṟamākat tōḻi yāṟṟāmai viyantatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en">1.This is how the confidante granted HIM a night tryst. 2. This how the confidante wondered about [HER] lack of strength while [HE] was behind the fence.</p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="NA49">
<l>            paṭutirai koḻīiya pāṉiṟa vekkart</l>
<l>            toṭiyōr maṭinteṉat tuṟaipulam piṉṟē</l>
<l>            muṭivalai mukanta muṭaṅkiṟāp paravaip</l>
<l>            paṭupuḷ ḷōppaliṟ pakaṉmāyn taṉṟē</l>
<l>            kōṭṭumī ṉeṟinta vuvakaiyar vēṭṭamaṭin </l>
<l>            temaru malkiṉa rēmārn taṉameṉac</l>
<l>            ceṉṟunā maṟiyi ṉevaṉō tōḻi</l>
<l>            maṉṟap puṉṉai mācciṉai naṟuvī</l>
<l>            muṉṟiṟ ṟāḻaiyoṭu kamaḻun</l>
<l>            teṇkaṭaṟ cērppaṉvāḻ ciṟunal lūrkkē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The ghat became lonely because those with bracelets have dozed of,</l>
<l rend="indent">the milk-coloured dunes enriched with coming waves.</l>
<l>Midday passed by in chasing away the birds falling</l>
<l rend="indent">into the spread of prawn drawn with knotted nets.</l>
<l rend="indent">Thinking “our people stay, having dozed of after the hunt, </l>
<l rend="indent">full of pleasure about the swordfish they had thrown up. We are full of joy,”</l>
<l>what, friend, if we went [and] found out,</l>
<l>– to the thriving little good village</l>
<l rend="indent3">of the man from the coast of the clear sea,</l>
<l>where the fragrant blossoms on the big branches of the Puṉṉai tree</l>
<l>on the village common emit fragrance together with the Tāḻai tree</l>
<l rend="indent4">in [his] front yard?</l>
        </lg>
         </div>
          </body>
